Definition: preoccupied with the pursuit of pleasure and especially games of chance
Example: led a dissipated life; a betting man; a card-playing son of a bitch; a gambling fool; sporting gents and their ladies
Synonyms: betting, card-playing, sporting, preoccupied, with, the, pursuit, of, pleasure, and, especially, games, chance, led, a, life, man, son, bitch, gambling, fool, gents, their, ladies
Category: adj.all
